  "url": "https://docs.atlassian.com",
  "description": "Documentation for pump specifications"
}
\`\`\`
Expected Output: The newly created Web Link with its ID and self link",
    "inputSchema": [
      "description",
      "testCaseKey",
      "url",
    ],
    "outputSchema": [
      "id",
      "self",
    ],
    "title": "Zephyr: Create Test Case Web Link",
  },
