\`\`\`json
{
  "issueKey": "PROJ-123"
}
\`\`\`
Expected Output: The List of test executions linked to Jira issue PROJ-123 with their keys and versions",
    "inputSchema": [
      "issueKey",
    ],
    "outputSchema": undefined,
    "title": "Zephyr: Get test executions linked to a Jira issue",
  },
